                    <li><Link to="/appointments">üìÖ ‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ô‡∏±‡∏î‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏¢</Link></li>
                    <li><Link to="/payments">üí≥ ‡∏ä‡∏≥‡∏£‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô</Link></li>
                    <li><Link to="/payouts">üí∏ ‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏à‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢</Link></li>
